rator type="small" position="left" up="7" down="13"][vc_column_text]\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Our Commercial moving team is dedicated to moving your business&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_column_text]Our commercial moving team specializes in jobs of all sizes. Sir Austin understands that his commercial customers often need different services than in residential moves and he\'s prepared a suite of services to take the headache out of moving. Not only do we offer specialized services and rates but we also offer ongoing corporate accounts that making paying for your move effortless. Whether you\'re moving a business across town of across country our commercial moving team has you covered![/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="42" down="0"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="42" down="0"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="684" img_size="1000x600" qode_css_animation=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="34" css_animation=""][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n&lt;h2 style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://siraustinmovers.com/long-distance-moving"&gt;Long Distance Moving&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" up="7" down="13"][vc_column_text]\r\n&lt;h4&gt;We have an entire team dedicated to long distance moves&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_column_text]Sir Austin understands that moving can be a pain, especially when you\'re moving long distances. Long distance moves are usually multi day affairs that require extra special attention to detail and that\'s why we\'ve created a specialized team within our company that only handles our long distance moves. We also have an awesome flat rate pricing schedule that ensures you know exactly what your move is going to cost so there are no hidden fees. The last thing you want is to have a move cost hundreds, if not thousands, more than it should. Give us a call for an awesome quote for your next long distance move.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="42" down="0"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="42" down="0"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="697" img_size="1000x650" qode_css_animation=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" background_color="#ffffff" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="34" css_animation=""][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n&lt;h2 style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;a href="http://siraustinmovers.com/storage"&gt;STORAGE SOLUTIONS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" up="7" down="13"][vc_column_text]\r\n&lt;h4&gt;Sir Austin provides the most innovative storage solutions on the market&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_column_text]We offer a number of different in-house and 3rd party storage solutions that can handle all your storage needs. Whether you\'re needing self storage, POD storage or long term storage, Sir Austin has a creative solution that will alleviate any storage problem you may have. Regardless of the solution needed, you can rest assured that we can handle the entire process for you, even if you choose a self storage option. Deciding on the proper solution will change from situation to situation but regardless of the problem, Sir Austin has a tailored made storage solution that will fit your budget.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="667" img_size="1000x650" qode_css_animation=""][/v