5" down="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" background_color="#ffffff" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="34" css_animation=""][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://siraustinmovers.com/business-relocations">Business Relocations</a></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" up="7" down="13"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Our commercial team handles business relocations of any size</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_column_text]Moving a business of any size can be a daunting task but it doesn\'t have to be stressful. A perfectly planned and executed business relocation can alleviate additional stress that moving to a new location includes. The last thing Sir Austin wants is for his customers to stress so sit back, get ready to plan because we are about to have a flawless move.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="42" down="0"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="725" img_size="1000x600" qode_css_animation=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="34" css_animation=""][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Business Accounts</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" up="7" down="13"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>We offer long term business accounts and credit</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_column_text]At Sir Austin Movers we understand that businesses are in an ongoing need for moving services and we\'ve devised a business account system that will allow business owners to pay only once a month instead of per job. A few hours here, a few hours there can lead to big savings and discounts. Our business account system allows for us to charge much less per job than we normally would, all based off of doing smaller jobs.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="42" down="0"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="908" img_size="1000x600" qode_css_animation=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" background_color="#ffffff" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="34" css_animation=""][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Specialty Moves</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" up="7" down="13"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Some say Sir Austins decedents were the ones who moved Stonehenge</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_column_text]While just a folk tale to many, some experts have directly linked Sir Austin to the tribe of people who moved Stonehenge. Although Sir is mute on the subject, it is widely believed that he learned the secret of how they were able to move such large amounts of stone over vast planes from a great uncle. A secret that he has kept to this day. Let\'s just say if Sir has learned the secrets of Stonehenge then your specialty move should be no problem.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="42" down="0"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="909" img_size="1000x600" qode_css_animation=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="87" css_animation=""][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Get Social With Sir Austin</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="center"