(52, 1, '2016-11-10 20:38:22', '2016-11-10 20:38:22', '[vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" background_color="#ffffff" padding_top="50" padding_bottom="81" css_animation=""][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">AUSTIN POOL TABLE MOVERS</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="center" up="7" down="35"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">Sir Austin used to shoot a little side pocket so he knows how valuable your pool table is</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="48" down="0"][qode_circles columns="five_columns" circle_line="no_line"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-cloud-download" size="fa-4x" title="Measuring" text="Whenever moving a pool table you want to take accurate measurement and chart the course of the move. It\'s important to measure out every step to make it will fit"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-laptop" size="fa-4x" title="Protecting" text="Whenever moving something the size of a pool table it is important to protect every square inch. This ensures maximum protection for your baby grand"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-signal" size="fa-4x" title="Moving" text="Although moving your table should be charted well before it\'s moved, sometimes unexpected issues can occur. That\'s why it\'s best to go with a company that specializes in pool table moving"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-arrow-circle-o-right" size="fa-4x" title="Unloading" text="Unloading a pool table is a cautious process. A wrong step and the next thing you know you have an unexpected scratch. But not on Sir Austin\'s watch"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-camera" size="fa-4x" title="Stripping" text="The final step in moving a pool table is to strip it of all pads and protection and move it in to place. We\'ll get you concert ready, even if you\'re only playing for your family"][/qode_circles][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" background_color="#323232" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="2" css_animation=""][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">HIRING A POOL TABLE MOVING COMPANY</span></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="center" color="#ffffff" up="7" down="37"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">Here\'s a few things to consider when hiring a company to move your pool table</span></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="55" down="2"][vc_row_inner row_type="row" type="full_width" text_align="left" css_animation="" padding="10"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][icon_text box_type="normal" icon="fa-camera-retro" icon_type="circle" icon_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="DO THEY SPECIALIZE IN POOL TABLES" separator="no" text="If a company isn\'t advertising for something then they generally do specialize in the service. Make sure to check if they outline their process somewhere on their website to ensure they are legit" icon_color="#ffffff" title_color="#ffffff" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="40" down="0"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][icon_text box_type="normal" icon="fa-hdd-o" icon_type="circle" icon_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="HOW WOULD THEY MOVE YOURS" separator="no" text="Most companies will come to your home and give you a free estimate on the moving fees. Asking them while they\'re there about the process they would employ should tell you all you need to know" icon_color="#ffffff" title_color="#ffffff" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="40" down="0"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner row_type="row" type="full_width" text_align="left" css_animation="" padding="10"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][icon_text box_type="normal" icon="fa-bell-o" icon_type="circle" icon_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="HOW MANY HAVE THEY MOVED" separator="no" text="Another good way to tell if the company in question has experience with moving pool tables. If they don\'t answer with an emphatic yes then chances are they don\'t specialize in the service" icon_color="#ffffff" title_color="#ffffff" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="40" down="0"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][icon_text box_type="normal" icon="fa-rocket" icon_type="circle" icon_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="WHAT IS THEIR PROCESS" separator="no" text="If a company really specializes in moving pool tables then they should have a process outlined for how it\'s done. If they don\'t have a process then they haven\'t been thinking about it, or doing it!" icon_color="#ffffff" title_color="#ffffff" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="40" down="0"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner row_type="row" type="full_width" text_align="left" css_animation="" padding="10"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][icon_text box_type="normal" icon="fa-bell-o" icon_type="circle" icon_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="WHAT DOES INSURANCE COVER" separator="no" text="Because nothing in life is guaranteed accidents do happen. A major question you need to ask is what does the insurance policy cover? Most of the time it\'s a fraction of what your pool table costs" icon_color="#ffffff" title_color="#ffffff" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="40" down="0"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][icon_text box_type="normal" icon="fa-rocket" icon_type="circle" icon_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="DO YOU PLAY POOL?" separator="no" text="Ok the last question shouldn\'t matter but it does to Sir Austin. For some weird reason he\'s suspicious of anyone who doesn\'t like playing pool, I mean come on, who doesn\'t like playing pool?" icon_color="#ffffff" title_color="#ffffff" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="40" down="0"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator type="transparent" up="55" down="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="87" css_animation=""][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Tune Into The Long Distance Sir Austin Channels</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="center" up="7" down="37"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">Connect with Sir Austin when you\'re on that long distance move</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="55" down="0"][qode_circles columns="five_columns" circle_line="with_line" line_color="#f1f1f1"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-facebook" size="fa-4x" border_width="8" icon_color="#ffffff" background_color="#cfcfcf" border_color="#f1f1f1"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-twitter" size="fa-4x" border_width="8" icon_color="#ffffff" background_color="#cfcfcf" border_color="#f1f1f1"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-google-plus" size="fa-4x" border_width="8" icon_color="#ffffff" background_color="#cfcfcf" border_color="#f1f1f1"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-linkedin" size="fa-4x" border_width="8" icon_color="#ffffff" background_color="#cfcfcf" border_color="#f1f1f1"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-instagram" size="fa-4x" border_width="8" icon_color="#ffffff" background_color="#cfcfcf" border_color="#f1f1f1"][/qode_circles][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Pool Table Moving', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'pool-table-moving', '', '', '2016-11-10