(90, 1, '2016-11-10 21:36:20', '2016-11-10 21:36:20', '[vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" background_color="#ffffff" padding_top="50" padding_bottom="81" css_animation=""][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING AND LOGISTICS</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="center" up="7" down="35"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">Sir Austin is in it for the long haul so a long distance move is a walk in the park for him</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="48" down="0"][qode_circles columns="five_columns" circle_line="no_line"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-cloud-download" size="fa-4x" title="International" text="We offer a number of different international shipping options. No load is too big or small for us to ship. We handle the entire shipping process for you."][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-laptop" size="fa-4x" title="Cargo" text="If you\'re in need to ship large cargo containers then we have a special solution just for you. Our cargo team will create a custom shipping solution just for you."][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-signal" size="fa-4x" title="Vehicles" text="If you\'re going out of the country then having to rent or buy a car once you arrive at your destination can be a pain. We\'ll ship your car anywhere in the world."][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-arrow-circle-o-right" size="fa-4x" title="Belongings" text="Moving out of the country? Well then don\'t trust the transport to just any moving company. Go with the Sir Austin pros that know moving and shipping!"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-camera" size="fa-4x" title="Trucking" text="If you\'re in constant need to ship items across the country then we have a special team dedicated to your needs. We\'ll truck your belongings anywhere in the world!"][/qode_circles][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" background_color="#323232" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="2" css_animation=""][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">LONG DISTANCE MOVING PROCESS</span></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="center" color="#ffffff" up="7" down="37"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">When it comes to long distance moves, Sir Austin is in it for the long haul</span></h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="55" down="2"][vc_row_inner row_type="row" type="full_width" text_align="left" css_animation="" padding="10"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][icon_text box_type="normal" icon="fa-camera-retro" icon_type="circle" icon_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="ASSESSING YOUR SHIPPING NEEDS" separator="no" text="The first step in creating a shipping plan is assessing your shipping needs. What type of items are being shipping and where to will effect the answers to these questions." icon_color="#ffffff" title_color="#ffffff" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="40" down="0"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][icon_text box_type="normal" icon="fa-hdd-o" icon_type="circle" icon_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="MAPPING YOUR SHIPPING ROUTE" separator="no" text="After you\'ve assessed your needs the next step is to map out your shipping routes. Is half or your cargo going here and the other half there? Mapping out a route will answer these questions." icon_color="#ffffff" title_color="#ffffff" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="40" down="0"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner row_type="row" type="full_width" text_align="left" css_animation="" padding="10"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][icon_text box_type="normal" icon="fa-bell-o" icon_type="circle" icon_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="PLANNING OUT THE LOGISTICS" separator="no" text="Logistics are the most complicated part of the shipping process. If you\'re a newb at logistical thinking then when you\'re business grows it can be hard to manage." icon_color="#ffffff" title_color="#ffffff" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="40" down="0"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][icon_text box_type="normal" icon="fa-rocket" icon_type="circle" icon_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="SHIPPING YOUR CARGO" separator="no" text="The next step in the process is to physically ship your goods. If you\'re shipping fragile items then trusting this part of the process is ill advised. Go with the shipping pros that know!" icon_color="#ffffff" title_color="#ffffff" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="40" down="0"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner row_type="row" type="full_width" text_align="left" css_animation="" padding="10"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][icon_text box_type="normal" icon="fa-bell-o" icon_type="circle" icon_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="DELIVERING YOUR CARGO" separator="no" text="Once your cargo arrives at it\'s destination then the next step is to deliver it to the intended recipient. We have lots of practice at this part so we can handle everything for you." icon_color="#ffffff" title_color="#ffffff" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="40" down="0"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][icon_text box_type="normal" icon="fa-rocket" icon_type="circle" icon_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="MANAGING THE SHIPPING PROCESS" separator="no" text="Once we create a custom shipping plan for your business our shipping team can manage 