con_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="BOXING AND PACKING" separator="no" text="A poorly packed box will not only damage your boxes but also damage your things. Sir Austin\'s favorite game growing up was Tetris, need we say more" icon_color="#ffffff" title_color="#ffffff" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="40" down="0"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][icon_text box_type="normal" icon="fa-rocket" icon_type="circle" icon_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="TRANSPORTATION PROCESS" separator="no" text="It\'s one thing to produce the perfect pack, but it\'s another to actually transport those items. Sir Austin is a seasoned vet at transportation so sit back and enjoy the ride!" icon_color="#ffffff" title_color="#ffffff" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="40" down="0"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner row_type="row" type="full_width" text_align="left" css_animation="" padding="10"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][icon_text box_type="normal" icon="fa-bell-o" icon_type="circle" icon_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="UNPACKING SERVICES" separator="no" text="If you don\'t pack a moving truck properly then be prepared for a chaotic unpacking. That\'s why Sir meticulously labels and inventories all of your belongings." icon_color="#ffffff" title_color="#ffffff" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="40" down="0"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][icon_text box_type="normal" icon="fa-rocket" icon_type="circle" icon_position="left" icon_size="fa-3x" use_custom_icon_size="no" title="FINALIZING YOUR MOVE" separator="no" text="Our moving services don\'t stop at unpacking your move. We have a thorough checklist that we follow to ensure that your entire new house is setup properly." icon_color="#ffffff" title_color="#ffffff" text_color="#ffffff"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="40" down="0"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator type="transparent" up="55" down="2"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="34" css_animation=""][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://siraustinmovers.com/residential-moving">RESIDENTIAL MOVING</a></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" up="7" down="13"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Our residential movers elevate the term white glove to a whole new meaning</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_column_text]Our residential moving team specializes in home and apartment moves. We understand that moving can be a daunting process but it doesn\'t have to be and our team goes the distance to make you as comfortable as possible the entire time. From taking full inventory of everything you are moving to properly labeling all packed boxes to ensure they end up in the right room during your move, we bend over backward to have as seamless a move as possible.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="112" img_size="1000x600" alignment="center" style="vc_box_rounded" qode_css_animation=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" background_color="#ffffff" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="34" css_animation=""][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://siraustinmovers.com/commercial-moving">COMMERCIAL MOVING</a></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" up="7" down="13"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Our Commercial moving team is dedicated to moving your business</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_column_text]Our commercial moving team specializes in jobs of all sizes. Sir Austin understands that his commercial customers often need different services than in residential moves and he\'s prepared a suite of services to take the headache out of moving. Not only do we offer specialized services and rates but we also offer ongoing corporate accounts that making paying for your move effortless. Whether you\'re moving a business across town of across country our commercial moving team has you covered![/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="42" down="0"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="42" down="0"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="107" img_size="1000x600" qode_css_animation=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="34" css_animation=""][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://siraustinmovers.com/long-distance-moving">Long Distance Moving</a></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" up="7" down="13"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>We have an entire team dedicated to long distance moves</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_column_text]Sir Austin understands that moving can be a pain, especially when you\'re moving long distances. Long distance moves are usually multi day affairs that require extra special attention to detail and that\'s why we\'ve created a specialized team within our company that only handles our long distance moves. We also have an awesome flat rate pricing schedule that ensures you know exactly what your move is going to cost so there are no hidden fees. The last thing you want is to have a move cost hundreds, if not thousands, more than it should. Give us a call for an awesome quote for your next long distance move.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="42" down="0"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="42" down="0"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="697" img_size="1000x650" qode_css_animation=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" background_color="#ffffff" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="34" css_animation=""][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://siraustinmovers.com/storage">STORAGE SOLUTIONS</a></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" up="7" down="13"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Sir Austin provides the most innovative storage solutions on the market</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_column_text]We offer a number of different in-house and 3rd party storage solutions that can handle all your storage needs. Whether you\'re needing self storage, POD storage or long term storage, Sir Austin has a creative solution that will alleviate any storage problem you may have. Regardless of the solution needed, you can rest assured that we can handle the entire process for you, even if you choose a self storage option. Deciding on the proper solution will change from situation to situation but regardless of the problem, Sir Austin has a tailored made storage solution that will fit your budget.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="667" img_size="1000x650" qode_css_animation=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" padding_top=