column_text]From large item storage units to warehousing our commercial storage and logistics team works with your business to devise a custom storage solution that is guaranteed to meet your needs. Sir Austin understands that every business is different and therefore every business has different storage needs. Give Sir a call so we can revolutionize your business with a custom storage solution![/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="42" down="0"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="107" img_size="1000x600" alignment="center" qode_css_animation=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" background_color="#ffffff" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="34" css_animation=""][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Document Storage</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" up="7" down="13"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Clear some space with our document storage and retrieval services</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_column_text]Our document storage and retrieval team gives you 24 hour access to all your businesses documents. If you\'re company generates a lot of documentation then it can be a pain to manage all of them in house. Document storage is not a complex business, but one that definitely takes some forethought not to mention whenever you want to retrieve something you have to rely on your companies filing methods. Skip the headache and let our team manage all your documents![/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="42" down="0"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="133" img_size="1200x700" alignment="center" qode_css_animation=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_i