" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="34" css_animation=""][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;"><a href="http://siraustinmovers.com/residential-moving">RESIDENTIAL MOVING</a></h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" up="7" down="13"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Our residential movers elevate the term white glove to a whole new meaning</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_column_text]Our residential moving team specializes in home and apartment moves. We understand that moving can be a daunting process but it doesn\'t have to be and our team goes the distance to make you as comfortable as possible the entire time. From taking full inventory of everything you are moving to properly labeling all packed boxes to ensure they end up in the right room during your move, we bend over backward to have as seamless a move as possible.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="112" img_size="1000x600" alignment="center" style="vc_box_rounded" qode_css_animation=""][/vc_column][/vc_row]\r\n\r\n[vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" background_color="#ffffff" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="34" css_animation=""][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: left;">Residential Moving</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="left" up="7" down="13"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4>Our Residential Moving Team Handles Your Entire Move</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="24" down="0"][vc_column_text]Our turnkey residential moving service is designed to handle an entire move for you from start to finish. The service includes everything that is related to moving you from one location to another and we mean everything. We start out by wrapping and packing your biggest items first. The items include couches, bedding, electronics, etc. Each item is professionally wrapped and packed ensuring total protection of your belongings. Next we box and pack the rest of your items, load up the truck and transport.[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="42" down="0"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="154" img_size="1000x600" qode_css_animation=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type="row" use_row_as_full_screen_section="no" type="grid" angled_section="no" text_align="left" background_image_as_pattern="without_pattern" padding_top="87" padding_bottom="87" css_animation=""][vc_column][vc_column_text]\r\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">GET SOCIAL WITH SIR AUSTIN</h2>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="small" position="center" up="7" down="37"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h4 style="text-align: center;">Get Jiggy with Sir Austin on one of his social channels</h4>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator type="transparent" up="55" down="0"][qode_circles columns="five_columns" circle_line="with_line" line_color="#f1f1f1"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-facebook" size="fa-4x" border_width="8" icon_color="#ffffff" background_color="#cfcfcf" border_color="#f1f1f1"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-twitter" size="fa-4x" border_width="8" icon_color="#ffffff" background_color="#cfcfcf" border_color="#f1f1f1"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-google-plus" size="fa-4x" border_width="8" icon_color="#ffffff" background_color="#cfcfcf" border_color="#f1f1f1"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-linkedin" size="fa-4x" border_width="8" icon_color="#ffffff" background_color="#cfcfcf" border_color="#f1f1f1"][qode_circle type="icon_type" icon="fa-instagram" size="fa-4x" border_width="8" icon_color="#ffffff" background_color="#cfcfcf" border_color="#f1f1f1"][/qode_circles][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Residential Moving', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'c